docker search nginx
docker pull nginx:latest
docker images
    docker run -P  -d nginx
    docker ps
OR
    docker run -p 8080:80 -d nginx
    docker ps
    
    
NOTE:    
what if run ::  docker run -d nginx 
Ans : container will spin up but you not able browse , all over mean the puspose of spinning up vanished coz 
     no port mapping of container port 80(default port of nginx to serve webpage) to hosts any port.
     
     you can verify by :
                        docker ps
